## New Project: inquire
- **Replaces:** AlecAivazis/survey (3,089 importers, 4.1k stars, archived Apr 2024, last release v2.3.7 Dec 2022) AND manifoldco/promptui (3,470 importers, 6.1k stars, unmaintained, last release v0.9.0 Oct 2021)
- **Why:** Combined ~6,500 importers. Both abandoned. No maintained drop-in replacement — charmbracelet/huh uses fundamentally different Elm/bubbletea architecture requiring full rewrite. go-prompt is REPL-style (different use case).
- **Package:** github.com/agentine/inquire (verified available)
- **Features:** Input, Multiline, Password, Confirm, Select, MultiSelect, Editor prompts. Functional options API. Structured Ask() form API.
- **Improvements:** context.Context support, generics (SelectTyped[T]), zero dependencies, better Windows Console API support, screen reader accessibility
- **Compat layers:** inquire/compat/survey (survey/v2 API), inquire/compat/promptui (promptui API)
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #773 (scaffolding), #774 (terminal I/O), #775 (core prompts), #776 (survey compat), #777 (promptui compat + tests)

